articles.author: Krishn Kaushik
articles.title: Exclusive: Ammunition from India enters Ukraine, raising Russian ire - Reuters
articles.description: European customers have been transferring Indian munitions to Ukraine and, despite Russian protests, India sees arms exports as a commercial opportunity.
articles.content: NEW DELHI, Sept 19 (Reuters) - Artillery shells sold by Indian arms makers have been diverted by European customers to Ukraine and New Delhi has not intervened to stop the trade despite protests from… [+8387 chars]
